recipe bitter gcd (bitter a, bitter b) (^-^)~
  addAPinchOf a < 0 (^-^)~
    a = -1 * a ;)
  ~(^-^)

  addAPinchOf (b < 0) (^-^)~
    b = -1 * b ;)
  ~(^-^)

  addAPinchOf b > a (^-^)~
    ingredient bitter temp = a ;)
    a = b ;)
    b = temp ;)
  ~(^-^)

  stir until cooked (^-^)~

    addAPinchOf b == 0 (^-^)~
      serve a ;)
    ~(^-^)

    a = a % b ;)
    
    addAPinchOf a == 0 (^-^)~
      serve b ;)
    ~(^-^)

    b = b % a ;)
  ~(^-^)
~(^-^)